                </exhotlnk>
            </para>
            <para>
                <exhotlnk document="../recalls/Cus04502rem.pdf" bookname="RECALL">Print ready (PDF file) copy of the
                    customer letter
                </exhotlnk>
            </para>
            <para>THIS IS AN
                <emph type="boldital">ISIS ONLY</emph>
                NOTIFICATION.
            </para>
            <para>There will be NO Dealer Mailing for this RECALL REMINDER.</para>
            <para>Please refer to the dealer letter G-04502 for service instructions.</para>
            <para>International has decided that a defect related to motor vehicle safety exists in
                <emph type="bold">certain</emph>
                front axle
                <emph type="bold">unitized wheel hubs</emph>
                of 4000, 8000, and 9000 Series trucks built 1/9/1998 through 12/31/2002.
            </para>
        </defect>
        <ownernote>
            <para>This letter is to inform you that the
                <emph type="italic">owners</emph>
                of suspect vehicles who have not completed the Recall Service Procedure have been sent a reminder to
                schedule an appointment to have the service performed.
            </para>
            <para>We appreciate your patience and cooperation regarding this campaign and apologize for any
                inconvenience this may cause.
